        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 7 at 10:06PM CDT until July 7 at 10:45PM CDT by NWS Hastings NE</headline>
        <description>At 1006 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located over Spalding, or
17 miles west of Albion, moving northeast at 30 mph.

HAZARD...Ping pong ball size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...People and animals outdoors will be injured. Expect damage
to roofs, siding, windows, and vehicles.

This severe thunderstorm will remain over mainly rural areas of
northeastern Greeley County.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
